<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q23_v6_item" title="Q23_v6" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Registro del caso:</p>
    <p>Registro de cambios: valor inicial = 23 940; cambio 1 = +8%; cambio 2 = +8%.</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        Se obtiene restando el 8 % de 23 940 a 23 940.
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Restar el 8 % de 23 940 da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1&#160;915,2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22&#160;024,8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Pero si un valor aumenta 8 %, el resultado queda multiplicado por <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,08</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>; por eso, para recuperar el valor anterior desde 23 940, debe cumplirse <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>1,08</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, no una resta directa.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        Se obtiene dividiendo 23 940 por 1,08 (o, equivalentemente,
        calculando
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn>
            <m:mo>·</m:mo>
            <m:mn>100</m:mn>
            <m:mo>/</m:mo>
            <m:mn>108</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        ).
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si un valor anterior es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>V</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>, después de aumentar 8 % queda <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,08</m:mn><m:mi>V</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces debe cumplirse <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,08</m:mn><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, de donde <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>1,08</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>108</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22&#160;166,666…</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Además, al verificar, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>22&#160;166,666…</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>1,08</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        Se obtiene sumando el 8 % de 23 940 a 23 940.
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Sumar el 8 % de 23 940 da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1&#160;915,2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>25&#160;855,2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Ese cálculo produce un valor mayor que 23 940, pero para deshacer un aumento de 8 % se debe encontrar un número que, al multiplicarse por <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,08</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, entregue exactamente 23 940.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        Se obtiene dividiendo 23 940 por 8 y multiplicando por 100,
        es decir, calculando
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn>
            <m:mo>/</m:mo>
            <m:mn>8</m:mn>
            <m:mo>·</m:mo>
            <m:mn>100</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>.
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Ese cálculo da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2&#160;992,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>299&#160;250</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, que no corresponde al valor buscado. Para deshacer un aumento de 8 %, no se divide por 8 y multiplica por 100; se divide por <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,08</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, porque el aumento transforma el valor original en <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>108</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> del valor inicial.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Representar el aumento de 8 %</strong></p>
            <p>Si un valor original es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>V</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>, al aumentar 8 % queda:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1,08</m:mn><m:mi>V</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Plantear la ecuación con 23 940</strong></p>
            <p>Para recuperar el valor anterior al aumento, debe cumplirse:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,08</m:mn><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Despejar el valor original</strong></p>
            <p>Dividimos ambos lados por <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,08</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>1,08</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Esto es equivalente a:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>108</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22&#160;166,666…</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar</strong></p>
            <p>Si multiplicamos este valor por <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1,08</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, obtenemos nuevamente 23 940:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>22&#160;166,666…</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>1,08</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23&#160;940</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La forma correcta de obtener el valor anterior es dividir 23 940 por 1,08. Por lo tanto, la alternativa correcta es la <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>